title: Steel Production for Great Britain
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1868-1924 (2)--Original Data, 1915-1938. Data Represent Steel Ingots Plus Castings. Source: National Federation Of Iron And Steel Manufacturers, Data For 1915-1933: Statistics Of The Iron And Steel Industries, 1934, P. 9. Data For 1934-1938: Iron And Steel Trades Special Review, 1938.

This NBER data series a01183bb appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
